Iterable<HorizontalLabelContainer.LabelInfo<T>>
public class HorizontalLabelContainer<T>
extends Object
implements Iterable<HorizontalLabelContainer.LabelInfo<T>>

Container of axis labels. This class collects all the labels that are to be displayed on an horizontal chart axis, making sure that no label overlaps another, taking into account the label width in pixel. Overloading labels are removed.
